response.overview: Based on the autobiographical novel, the tempestuous 6-year relationship between Liberace and his (much younger) lover, Scott Thorson, is recounted.
response.tagline: Too much of a good thing is wonderful.
response.title: Behind the Candelabra

titles.title: Liberace - Zu viel des Guten ist wundervoll
